Let $$ W $$ be a subspace of $$ \mathbb{R}^n $$ and $$ dim W = k, $$ $$ W = span\{x_1, x_2, \dots,x_k\} $$
 $$  $$  $$ \hat{v} \in W $$closest to $$ v $$

