>   $$ \bigg\vert A - \lambda I \bigg\vert = \bigg\vert\matrix{ 2-\lambda & 1+i \cr 1-i & 3-\lambda }\bigg\vert = (2-\lambda)(3-\lambda)-(1+i)(1-i) = 0 $$

>   $$ \implies \lambda^2 -5\lambda + 6 -2 = 0$$

